{"audioUrl": "", "duration": 127.173, "paragraphs": [{"id": "p1", "sentences": [{"id": "p1s1", "text": "¡Hola! Mi nombre es Lucas.", "boundaries": [{"text": "¡Hola! ", "start": 0.0, "end": 0.824}, {"text": "Mi ", "start": 0.998, "end": 1.126}, {"text": "nombre ", "start": 1.173, "end": 1.463}, {"text": "es ", "start": 1.509, "end": 1.591}, {"text": "Lucas.", "start": 1.672, "end": 2.287}]}, {"id": "p1s2", "text": "Yo tengo veinticinco años.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Yo ", "start": 2.879, "end": 3.007}, {"text": "tengo ", "start": 3.053, "end": 3.297}, {"text": "veinticinco ", "start": 3.344, "end": 3.901}, {"text": "años.", "start": 3.936, "end": 4.47}]}, {"id": "p1s3", "text": "Soy brasileño y vivo en la ciudad de San Pablo.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Soy ", "start": 5.062, "end": 5.259}, {"text": "brasileño ", "start": 5.294, "end": 6.06}, {"text": "y ", "start": 6.177, "end": 6.293}, {"text": "vivo ", "start": 6.351, "end": 6.571}, {"text": "en ", "start": 6.618, "end": 6.664}, {"text": "la ", "start": 6.722, "end": 6.792}, {"text": "ciudad ", "start": 6.838, "end": 7.152}, {"text": "de ", "start": 7.187, "end": 7.256}, {"text": "San ", "start": 7.303, "end": 7.43}, {"text": "Pablo.", "start": 7.488, "end": 8.115}]}, {"id": "p1s4", "text": "Mi casa es chica, pero es muy linda y cómoda.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Mi ", "start": 8.707, "end": 8.835}, {"text": "casa ", "start": 8.87, "end": 9.125}, {"text": "es ", "start": 9.183, "end": 9.265}, {"text": "chica, ", "start": 9.346, "end": 9.961}, {"text": "pero ", "start": 10.077, "end": 10.298}, {"text": "es ", "start": 10.344, "end": 10.426}, {"text": "muy ", "start": 10.484, "end": 10.646}, {"text": "linda ", "start": 10.681, "end": 10.983}, {"text": "y ", "start": 11.029, "end": 11.053}, {"text": "cómoda.", "start": 11.122, "end": 11.749}]}, {"id": "p1s5", "text": "Me gusta mucho mi ciudad porque tiene muchos parques.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Me ", "start": 12.341, "end": 12.458}, {"text": "gusta ", "start": 12.492, "end": 12.748}, {"text": "mucho ", "start": 12.794, "end": 13.096}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 13.154, "end": 13.247}, {"text": "ciudad ", "start": 13.27, "end": 13.63}, {"text": "porque ", "start": 13.7, "end": 13.932}, {"text": "tiene ", "start": 13.978, "end": 14.187}, {"text": "muchos ", "start": 14.245, "end": 14.605}, {"text": "parques.", "start": 14.663, "end": 15.65}]}, {"id": "p1s6", "text": "El clima acá es bueno.", "boundaries": [{"text": "El ", "start": 16.25, "end": 16.447}, {"text": "clima ", "start": 16.494, "end": 16.854}, {"text": "acá ", "start": 16.889, "end": 17.179}, {"text": "es ", "start": 17.26, "end": 17.365}, {"text": "bueno.", "start": 17.423, "end": 18.003}]}, {"id": "p1s7", "text": "Hoy el día está soleado y caluroso.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Hoy ", "start": 18.595, "end": 18.862}, {"text": "el ", "start": 18.897, "end": 18.99}, {"text": "día ", "start": 19.048, "end": 19.245}, {"text": "está ", "start": 19.303, "end": 19.559}, {"text": "soleado ", "start": 19.629, "end": 20.302}, {"text": "y ", "start": 20.395, "end": 20.464}, {"text": "caluroso.", "start": 20.522, "end": 21.347}]}]}, {"id": "p2", "sentences": [{"id": "p2s1", "text": "Yo vivo con mi familia.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Yo ", "start": 21.939, "end": 22.136}, {"text": "vivo ", "start": 22.194, "end": 22.438}, {"text": "con ", "start": 22.496, "end": 22.612}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 22.659, "end": 22.74}, {"text": "familia.", "start": 22.798, "end": 23.471}]}, {"id": "p2s2", "text": "Mi mamá se llama Maria y mi papá se llama João.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Mi ", "start": 24.064, "end": 24.191}, {"text": "mamá ", "start": 24.249, "end": 24.505}, {"text": "se ", "start": 24.574, "end": 24.667}, {"text": "llama ", "start": 24.69, "end": 24.969}, {"text": "Maria ", "start": 25.039, "end": 25.526}, {"text": "y ", "start": 25.642, "end": 25.759}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 25.828, "end": 25.909}, {"text": "papá ", "start": 25.968, "end": 26.235}, {"text": "se ", "start": 26.304, "end": 26.397}, {"text": "llama ", "start": 26.42, "end": 26.78}, {"text": "João.", "start": 26.815, "end": 27.396}]}, {"id": "p2s3", "text": "Mi mamá es profesora y mi papá es chofer.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Mi ", "start": 27.988, "end": 28.115}, {"text": "mamá ", "start": 28.162, "end": 28.464}, {"text": "es ", "start": 28.533, "end": 28.638}, {"text": "profesora ", "start": 28.696, "end": 29.346}, {"text": "y ", "start": 29.427, "end": 29.509}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 29.567, "end": 29.66}, {"text": "papá ", "start": 29.706, "end": 30.019}, {"text": "es ", "start": 30.089, "end": 30.182}, {"text": "chofer.", "start": 30.24, "end": 30.867}]}, {"id": "p2s4", "text": "Tengo una hermana menor.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Tengo ", "start": 31.459, "end": 31.773}, {"text": "una ", "start": 31.807, "end": 31.993}, {"text": "hermana ", "start": 32.04, "end": 32.446}, {"text": "menor.", "start": 32.504, "end": 33.073}]}, {"id": "p2s5", "text": "Su nombre es Ana.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Su ", "start": 34.358, "end": 34.555}, {"text": "nombre ", "start": 34.613, "end": 35.043}, {"text": "es", "start": 35.113, "end": 35.229}]}, {"id": "p2s6", "text": "Ana es estudiante.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Ana ", "start": 36.401, "end": 36.75}, {"text": "es", "start": 36.831, "end": 36.947}]}, {"id": "p2s7", "text": "Nosotros tenemos un perro grande.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Nosotros ", "start": 38.456, "end": 38.921}, {"text": "tenemos ", "start": 38.967, "end": 39.292}, {"text": "un ", "start": 39.408, "end": 39.466}, {"text": "perro", "start": 39.524, "end": 39.791}]}, {"id": "p2s8", "text": "El nombre del perro es Rex.", "boundaries": [{"text": "El ", "start": 40.999, "end": 41.161}, {"text": "nombre ", "start": 41.208, "end": 41.521}, {"text": "del ", "start": 41.556, "end": 41.672}, {"text": "perro ", "start": 41.742, "end": 42.125}, {"text": "es", "start": 42.206, "end": 42.369}]}, {"id": "p2s9", "text": "Él es muy feliz, rápido y juguetón.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Él ", "start": 43.623, "end": 43.797}, {"text": "es ", "start": 43.855, "end": 43.913}, {"text": "muy ", "start": 43.971, "end": 44.134}, {"text": "feliz, ", "start": 44.18, "end": 44.784}, {"text": "rápido ", "start": 44.935, "end": 45.457}, {"text": "y", "start": 45.538, "end": 45.585}]}]}, {"id": "p3", "sentences": [{"id": "p3s1", "text": "Todos los días, me despierto a las siete de la mañana.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Todos ", "start": 46.932, "end": 47.315}, {"text": "los ", "start": 47.384, "end": 47.547}, {"text": "días, ", "start": 47.593, "end": 47.965}, {"text": "me ", "start": 48.011, "end": 48.116}, {"text": "despierto ", "start": 48.151, "end": 48.638}, {"text": "a ", "start": 48.696, "end": 48.72}, {"text": "las ", "start": 48.766, "end": 48.905}, {"text": "siete ", "start": 48.94, "end": 49.277}, {"text": "de ", "start": 49.323, "end": 49.37}, {"text": "la", "start": 49.416, "end": 49.474}]}, {"id": "p3s2", "text": "Voy al baño y me lavo la cara.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Su ", "start": 50.658, "end": 50.855}, {"text": "nombre ", "start": 50.913, "end": 51.273}, {"text": "es ", "start": 51.331, "end": 51.436}, {"text": "Ana. ", "start": 51.552, "end": 52.028}, {"text": "Ana ", "start": 52.62, "end": 53.026}, {"text": "es", "start": 53.096, "end": 53.189}]}, {"id": "p3s3", "text": "Tomo café con leche y como pan con manteca.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Nosotros ", "start": 54.675, "end": 55.105}, {"text": "tenemos ", "start": 55.151, "end": 55.43}, {"text": "un ", "start": 55.511, "end": 55.557}, {"text": "perro ", "start": 55.615, "end": 55.848}, {"text": "grande. ", "start": 55.894, "end": 56.486}, {"text": "El", "start": 57.078, "end": 57.264}]}, {"id": "p3s4", "text": "Después, voy al trabajo en colectivo.", "boundaries": [{"text": "nombre ", "start": 57.334, "end": 57.647}, {"text": "del ", "start": 57.682, "end": 57.821}, {"text": "perro ", "start": 57.891, "end": 58.274}, {"text": "es ", "start": 58.367, "end": 58.53}, {"text": "Rex. ", "start": 58.704, "end": 59.249}, {"text": "Él ", "start": 59.841, "end": 60.062}, {"text": "es ", "start": 60.132, "end": 60.19}, {"text": "muy", "start": 60.259, "end": 60.422}]}, {"id": "p3s5", "text": "El viaje es largo.", "boundaries": [{"text": "rápido ", "start": 61.153, "end": 61.641}, {"text": "y", "start": 61.722, "end": 61.78}]}, {"id": "p3s6", "text": "Yo trabajo en una oficina.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Todos ", "start": 63.116, "end": 63.452}, {"text": "los ", "start": 63.51, "end": 63.661}, {"text": "días, ", "start": 63.708, "end": 64.184}, {"text": "me", "start": 64.276, "end": 64.404}]}, {"id": "p3s7", "text": "Mi trabajo empieza a las nueve y termina a las cinco de la tarde.", "boundaries": [{"text": "a ", "start": 64.973, "end": 64.996}, {"text": "las ", "start": 65.043, "end": 65.182}, {"text": "siete ", "start": 65.217, "end": 65.484}, {"text": "de ", "start": 65.53, "end": 65.6}, {"text": "la ", "start": 65.646, "end": 65.716}, {"text": "mañana. ", "start": 65.763, "end": 66.39}, {"text": "empieza ", "start": 66.924, "end": 67.47}, {"text": "a ", "start": 67.551, "end": 67.586}, {"text": "las ", "start": 67.655, "end": 67.806}, {"text": "nueve ", "start": 67.876, "end": 68.282}, {"text": "y ", "start": 68.607, "end": 68.724}, {"text": "termina ", "start": 68.782, "end": 69.246}, {"text": "a", "start": 69.327, "end": 69.362}]}, {"id": "p3s8", "text": "Me gusta mi trabajo.", "boundaries": [{"text": "cinco ", "start": 69.606, "end": 69.954}, {"text": "de ", "start": 70.001, "end": 70.047}, {"text": "la", "start": 70.094, "end": 70.163}]}]}, {"id": "p4", "sentences": [{"id": "p4s1", "text": "En mi tiempo libre, me gusta leer libros y escuchar música.", "boundaries": [{"text": "Me ", "start": 72.017, "end": 72.191}, {"text": "gusta ", "start": 72.214, "end": 72.493}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 72.539, "end": 72.609}, {"text": "trabajo. ", "start": 72.644, "end": 73.329}, {"text": "En ", "start": 73.921, "end": 74.06}, {"text": "mi ", "start": 74.095, "e